    {
      "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Wrapper (`ccw_*` / `tatara_wrapper_*`) agent-runtime metrics. Agent pods are EPHEMERAL and have no scrape target of their own: each pod pushes its `ccw_*` series to the operator's pushmetrics receiver (`POST /internal/metrics/push`), which Prometheus scrapes as `job=tatara-operator` WITHOUT honor_labels. So the agent's own pod/job labels are relabeled to `exported_pod`/`exported_job`, while plain `pod`/`job` are the operator scrape target itself. Agent identity is `exported_pod` (the pod name encodes project/repo/issue: `tatara-<project>-<gh|gl>-<repo>-<issue|mr>-<n>`). Filter with the `$pod` variable (it targets `exported_pod`). Per-run counters start fresh per pod and the whole series is TTL-evicted (default 5m - see `operator_pushed_runs` / `operator_pushed_runs_evicted_total` below) after a run's last push, so a turn's first increment can be under-counted and rate()/increase() windows here are kept >=5m (mostly 15m/30m) to survive that churn; idle-fleet panels legitimately read 0 or blank, not broken queries. Durable per-kind/repo/project token spend and USD cost live on `Tatara - Task Delivery` (`operator_task_tokens_total`); the token panel here is a wrapper-vantage cross-check only, not billing. `ccw_turn_cost_usd_total` is DEAD (result.json is never written, and it is absent from live Prometheus) so it is deliberately not dashboarded."
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "description": "Agent-reported platform problems: agents call the report_internal_issue MCP tool when they hit a platform defect, and the wrapper tailer meters them as tatara_wrapper_internal_issue_total{category,severity}. Highest-value panel on this dashboard: this signal was previously only visible via the Loki alert. A non-zero bar means an agent explicitly flagged a broken platform behavior during its run.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 60,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": {"legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false},
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": {"type": "linear"},
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": {"group": "A", "mode": "normal"},
            "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "off"}
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "min": 0,
          "noValue": "0",
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3},
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull", "max"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (category, severity) (increase(tatara_wrapper_internal_issue_total{exported_pod=~\"$pod\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{category}} / {{severity}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Agent-Reported Platform Problems (report_internal_issue)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
